 gm in felwithe.  He wants 4 bone chips first, then 4 ghoul hearts, then 2 heads and a box from LF.  I believe that these quests are broken though atm because of the new quests in lfay.  Kinda pisses me off.... I got the first 2, was going to upgrade them both to get the root and the disease/poison buff.. <p><a href=http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=39648>Farendil</a><BR>
