<a href=http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=10797>Rakizi Bubblefists</a><BR>
55th Iksar Master
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/udryas.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dryas</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC= http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/14/01 12:52:26 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Question about a peice of quest armor i have herd about...</span><hr size=1> Well, there is the Maple Leaf Mask from the Prince in PoG. I'm not sure if you can quest for it.  <br>
<br>
It does have a right click effect, of Tree Form.  So, in effect, it does root you....<br>
<br>
Dryas <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uwestorwarstalker.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Westor Warstalker</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/14/01 1:09:25 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> one more quests...</span><hr size=1> Thanks for the info, I found the guy, and i was wondering about the Ghoul hearts...  Ghoul hearts drop in Unrest, but they lore, and the guy wants 4...  I could get one... go to him and come back and get more 4 times... but i was wondering if those are even the right ones.  He said they came of ghasts in Lfay, but i ran all around lfay looking at track and nothing with the name of ghast came up...  So any info on that would be helpful. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uelawnah.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Elawnah</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://members.tripod.co.uk/redhotant/icons/iconoc11.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/14/01 1:27:02 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://elawnah.homestead.com/files/again....jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Question about a peice of quest armor i have herd about...</span><hr size=1> There's a new monster in Lesser Faydark called a rancerorus(sp?) ghast. They wander the zone, just track em down. They have less than 450hp as one Calefaction killed em. After ya turn in the 4 hearts, you'l get the first symbol. It casts Echeniciea (sp?) Infusion. (Adds +10 to PR and DR) hope that helps! <p><A><img src=http://elawnah.homestead.com/files/thingy.JPG height=156 width=392></A>

</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umanolas.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Manolas</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/15/01 2:41:21 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://manolasautumnleaf.homestead.com/files/dancing_sheep.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Question about a peice of quest armor i have herd about...</span><hr size=1> <br>
<br>
  The quest aren't broken because of the event in LFay.<br>
  Kill ghasts in LFay for 4 hearts, turn them in to the cleric<br>
  trainer in Felwithe. Then camp the undead ruins until a<br>
  named necromancer spawns (green as heck, he's around<br>
  level 20 or less). Kill him, loot his head. Killing him spawns<br>
  the delievery person at the MM zone which runs to the<br>
  inkey camp. Kill that person and loot head/box. Turn in<br>
  the previous medallion, both heads and the box to get<br>
  the next taliasman in line which casts Aloe Sweat <br>
  (+15pr/dr buff, stacks with everything, including the buff<br>
  from the first necklace if you do that quest again when<br>
  you get the second quest done). The third quest casts<br>
  the low level root spell, but nobody has done the 4th<br>
  part of the quest yet. Personally the 2nd medallion's effect<br>
  is much better than the 3rd's. At least I find it useful for<br>
  the added PR/DR since many things in SoV seem to use<br>
  poison or disease.<br>
<br>
  Manolas Autumnleaf<br>
  Druid of 59 seasons, Cazic Thule<br>
  Officer of Second Age <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uaubie.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aubie</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/15/01 9:04:15 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Question about a peice of quest armor i have herd about...</span><hr size=1> Maybe the quests aren't broken on CT...On Brell, the quest is BROKEN! The dark elf courier will NOT spawn afte killing the necro. Glad to here things are working on CT, but don't make a blanket statement about the quest not being broken on all servers without the facts.<br>
